Polymorph, an OpenGL screensaver for Windows.

See the uniform polyhedra! See them morph! See them spin! See them bounce!

Download page:

  https://buster.me.uk/

Instructions:

 * Download the screensaver from the download page.
 * Right-click on the screensaver file in File Explorer.
 * Click "Test", "Configure" or "Install".

See the file "LICENSE" for the conditions under which you may use this software.
See the file "INSTALL" for instructions on how to build from source.
